        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for AM’s kindness.</p>
            <p>CD did not understand him about "prepotency".</p>
            <p>With respect to cave animals CD believes that on reflection AM will admit "that on creation doctrine, there has been surprising diversity for such similar habitation".</p>
            <p>Has heard from A. von Keyserling who "makes no difficulty about imperfection of Geological Record".</p>
